name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AAMC MCAT Interface by Jack Westin

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows users who have purchased AAMC practice material to view it in the proper intended MCAT exam format.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows users who have AAMC practice material to view it in the proper intended MCAT exam format and provides highlight, strikethrough, next question, previous question functionality in order to best practice for the MCAT.
